  {
    "action": {
      "input": {
        "description": " The Network Revenue-Generating Hub is a functional spin\u2011off specializing in the Sales Function. It structures client relationships, monetizes IP derivatives, and generates revenue for the network.\n\nOperating as a customer\u2011facing OpCo, the RGH enables networks to offer services, licenses, or products without exposing the core network, governance bodies, or non\u2011commercial Hubs to contractual or regulatory risk. Revenue generated by the RGH can be distributed to the network in accordance with governance\u2011defined \nallocation rules.\n\n**Typical Use Cases**\n\n- Licensing of open\u2011source derivatives\n- Commercial service offerings by DAO\u2011adjacent teams\n- Frontend Hosting\n- Jurisdiction\u2011specific revenue activities\n\nSuitable for Networks that require a compliant, isolated commercial execution layer.\n",
        "lastModified": "2026-04-29T16:16:31.000Z",
        "summary": "The Commercial Hub of a Network Organization.\n",
        "thumbnailUrl": "https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ9ek-0IiHyQA5kwckg3A1bvrN4FdMzyA0O3w&s",
        "title": "Network Revenue Generating Hub"
